              ],
              "free_text": [
                "  plastic scintillation pairs detectors were",
                "used for determination the mass-to-charge ratio",
                "obtained from a time-of-flight measurement.",
                "The six time-projection chambers (TPC)"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Gamma-ray measurements were carried out with",
                "eight triple-cluster detectors of the MINIBALL gamma-",
                "ray spectrometer. Each cluster contains three HPGe",
                "crystals, which are subdivided into six azimuthal",
                "segments, providing the necessary granularity for",
                "performing the Doppler correction of the gamma-rays",
                "emitted in flight by the ejectile moving at",
                "relativistic velocity."
              ]
            }
